 Violence Offender Treatment Board, is <ln numlevel="1" lineno="46" slineno="1-24"/>repealed July 1, 2027.</subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-15" dnum="15-o:14-i" numlevel="1" lineno="47" slineno="1-25" level="1"><display><amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="1014" style="2" owner="o" level="1" deltag="both">(15)</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1015" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="both" space="true">(14)</amend></display>Section <xref depth="3" refnumber="63M-7-902">63M-7-902</xref>, Creation -- Membership -- Terms -- Vacancies -- Expenses, <ln numlevel="1" lineno="48" slineno="1-26"/>is repealed July 1, 2029.</subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-16" dnum="16-o:15-i" numlevel="1" lineno="49" slineno="1-27" level="1"><display><amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="1015" style="2" owner="o" level="1" deltag="both">(16)</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1016" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="both" space="true">(15)</amend></display>Title 63M, Chapter 11, Utah Commission on Aging, is repealed July 1, <amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="3" groupid="3" style="2" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" deltag="both">2026</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="2" groupid="2" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="both" space="true"><ln numlevel="1" lineno="50" slineno="1-28"/>2031</amend>.</subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-17" dnum="17-o:16-i" numlevel="1" lineno="51" slineno="1-29" level="1"><display><amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="1016" style="2" owner="o" level="1" deltag="both">(17)</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1017" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="both" space="true">(16)</amend></display>Title 63N, Chapter 2, Part 2, Enterprise Zone Act, is repealed July 1, 2028.</subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-18" dnu